# CHANGELOG

All notable changes to this Obsidian Attachment Cleaner plugin will be documented in this file.

The format is based on [Keep a Changelog](https://keepachangelog.com/zh-CN/1.0.0/),
and this project adheres to [Semantic Versioning](https://semver.org/lang/zh-CN/).

## [1.1.2] - 2026-03-12
### Changed
- 新增基于 Obsidian 官方 API 收集被引用附件路径的核心函数 `getAttachmentPathSetForVault`
- 新增忽略此文件选择

## [1.1.3] - 2026-03-13
### Changed
- 修改了部分UI设计
- 修改界面语言为中文